<paragraph blockId="0.[1225,1434,922,967]" box="[1225,1434,936,967]" pageId="0" pageNumber="348">• 60-110cm.</paragraph>
</caption>
<caption box="[1226,1570,1124,1162]" inLine="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="348" startId="0.[1226,1239,1124,1162]" targetBox="[219,1153,780,1400]" targetPageId="0">
<paragraph box="[1226,1570,1124,1162]" pageId="0" pageNumber="348">• Neotropical Region.</paragraph>
</caption>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="348">• Moist tropical and subtropical, lowland and sub-montane, and dry deciduous and semi-deciduous, forests, scrub and farmland-forest mosaics.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="348" type="description">
<paragraph box="[1226,1699,1290,1319]" pageId="0" pageNumber="348">• 3 genera, 29 species, 30 taxa.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="348">• 4 species Critically Endangered, 3 species Endangered, 2 species Vulnerable; none Extinct since 1600.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
